comments: The most interesting class I\'ve ever have. The most interesting teacher I\'ve ever met. Gues, take it...
Super chill guy. Reading are really interesting and as long as you do them, you will get an A. Def the kind of guy you would want to kick it with.

Jacob Hall is a great teacher. He isn\'t difficult at all as long as you do the homework. I had him for 20th century issues: Poverty in the US and Latin America and the class was easy. He gives you essay test questions before exams so its not bad at all. Find him as a teacher and you\'ll be satisfied.
He seems like the kind of guy you\'d want to have a beer with.
Good teacher not hard to get a A if you read the books
